Padre-Plugin-Autodia version 0.01
=================================

Padre plugin to integrate Autodia.

Provides an Autodia menu under 'plugins' with options to create UML diagrams for the current or selected files.

Development of initial release sponsered by Connected-uk (www.connected-uk.com)

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Autodia

